cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CE 

The paper discusses the application of AI and machine learning models for crop detection using earth observation data. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of state-of-the-art machine learning models, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The use of earth observation data for monitoring SDGs falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the proposed AI-based evaluative infrastructure for SDGs falls under the computer engineering (cs.CE) sub-category.
